&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Diabetes Specialist Dietitian&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Maternity leave cover – 9 months (with possible extension to 1 year) &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;£45,780 - £51,393 per annum incl. HCAS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chelsea&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; and Westminster Hospital&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced band 7 Dietitian to join our Diabetes and Endocrine team, to provide excellent inpatient and outpatient diabetes care. The post holder will provide clinical expertise both in inpatient and outpatient care, and will join a dynamic team based at Chelsea &amp; Westminster Hospital (and when required West Middlesex University Hospital).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a growing service meeting the needs of an expanding local population, the service provides a number of routine and specialist services, including; providing multidisciplinary clinic support, dietitian and nurse-led clinics, ante-natal and pre-conception clinic, insulin pump clinic, transition clinic, virtual clinic, CGMS, emergency reviews and managing routine and urgent ward referrals. We are also a DAFNE centre.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants should possess an in-depth clinical knowledge of diabetes, which should be supported by recent experience in caring for people with diabetes. In addition, excellent communication and clinical skills, time management skills and a commitment to evidence based practice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sara Shah, Chronic Disease Team Lead&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;sararasoul.shah@chelwest.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;0203 315 8161/8178&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Or&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Shweta Patel Diabetes Specialist Dietitian via email Shweta.Patel@chelwest.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
